title: Free Agency day 1 recap
itunes:title: Free Agency day 1 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler discuss the biggest deals from the first day of free agency, including Brock Osweiler heading to the Texans and Matt Forte joining the Jets. Then, the heroes end the show with a speed round with other news from the NFL.
